Introduction

Pattern (Korean: 패턴; Japanese: パターン) is a five-member boy group under S.I.E.T.E Entertainment. They debuted on November 23, 2018 with their first single album "Last Stage". They began their activities in Japan before debuting in South Korea. They debuted on October 17, 2022 in Korea with their single "Malibu".
